The "filter" property types take a string value, which will be parsed as a filter, and the results will be passed to the engine as an array. Any filter which isn't an empty string will be interpretted and returned, even if it produces zero results.

!! Context

Filter properties are interpretted with the context of every individual [[graph object widget|Graph Objects]] they are attached to, even if they're attached to a widget because of a parent <<.wlink PropertiesWidget>>.

!! Settings

String properties have no extra settings besides [[those allowed by all properties|Property Types]].
